text: "Daylight" is a 1985 song by Australian singer Jimmy Barnes. It is the third single from his debut studio album Bodyswerve. It went to number 12 in Australia. ==Track listing== 7" Single (K 9582) *Side A "Daylight" *Side B "Paradise" *Side C "Daylight" (Live) *Side D "Paradise" (Live) ==References== Category:1985 songs Category:Jimmy Barnes songs
title: Daylight (Jimmy Barnes song)
